Synnefo
=======

Installation
------------
    $ sudo easy_install virtualenv
    ....
    $ git clone https://user@code.grnet.gr/git/synnefo synnefo
    $ virtualenv synnefo --no-site-packages
    ...
    $ cd synnefo
    $ ./bin/pip install django django-piston django-localeurl
    ...
    ...
    $ cp settings.py.dist settings.py
    $ ../bin/python manage.py runserver


Alt - main
----------
To change between alt and main view, in ui/templates/home.html
    (line 7) change alt-main.css <-> main.css
    (line 24) href="alt-instances" <-> href="instances"
